{"service_name": "NHS INFORMATION GOVERNANCE FOR CLOUD SERVICES", "service_id": "4928212626833408", "company_name": "St Helens & Knowsley Teaching Hospitals NHS Trust", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     St Helens &amp; Knowsley Teaching Hospitals NHS Trust\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     NHS INFORMATION GOVERNANCE FOR CLOUD SERVICES\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Supporting NHS organisations to provide high quality care through the effective and appropriate use of information, maintaining comprehensive, accurate records and keeping records confidential and secure whilst using cloud technology..\r\n\r\nSpecialising in key elements - complex interaction of Data Protection, Freedom Of Information, Human Rights, Information Security and Confidentiality.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Consultation to understand the client\u2019s objectives.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Planning of timescales and resources\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Review existing solutions, policies,  and practices\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Data Collection to assess the current situation.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Site Visits to consult with key members of staff\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Final report and recommendations\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     On-going Managed Information Governance Service and Support available\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Collaborate with clients partners when required\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Support with NHS IG toolkit annual submission\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Support to all staff in the event of a breach\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Service provided by NHS staff ensuring expertise and knowledge\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Robust assurance of meeting or exceeding standard IG requirements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Greater transparency when there are breaches of information governance.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Appropriately tailored service to meet local priorities and requirements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Supporting and coordinating activities enabling continuous improvement\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Fostering NHS culture that values and utilises information effectively\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensures awareness of security, safety and confidentiality.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Consistency of interpretation of NHS IG policy or rules\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Addressing different cultures in respect of sharing information.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Assurance of compliance all relevant laws, direction and guidance\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3345 per unit per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/579561/4928212626833408-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/579561/4928212626833408-sfia-rate-card.pdf